Yemi Eberechi Alade had too much to show in an alluring picture she took and uploaded online. Some fans of Yemi Alade have been zooming this picture to see what looks like her panties. The beautiful singer who has links with the South-eastern part of Nigeria squatted as she posed for a picture. “What Are We having for dinner …#TurkeyNla #WOMANOFSTEEL” was the caption attached to the picture but many have been discussing the colour of her underwear which they believe was made of a local fabric called Ankara. Despite the comments, she has refused to take it down and it seems she might be enjoying the buzz it’s bring her. Source